# NotebookLM runtime (bundled Python + Playwright - too large for repo)
src-tauri/bin/notebooklm-runtime/**/*
!src-tauri/bin/notebooklm-runtime/.gitkeep
squashfs-root/
incrementum-tauri

# Android assets copied during build
src-tauri/gen/android/app/src/main/assets/

# Local plugin build outputs (Gradle/Kotlin compile artifacts). These are
# regenerated on every build; tracking them causes perpetual binary churn in
# release commits. Matches the build/ dirs under src-tauri/gen/android (already
# ignored) and keeps in-repo Tauri plugins clean.
src-tauri/plugins/*/android/build/
src-tauri/plugins/*/android/.gradle/
src-tauri/plugins/*/ios/build/

# Browser extension build artifacts (separate Node project + compiled .xpi).
# These are not part of the Tauri app and are regenerated from source on demand;
# tracking them would sweep unrelated files into release commits via `git add -A`.
*.xpi
browser_extension/

